WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:03.033
I thought you really let go of my uncle

2
00:00:03.700 --> 00:00:05.133
People who have been in love for the past ten years

3
00:00:05.133 --> 00:00:06.766
How could it be forgotten so easily?

4
00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:07.700
Want me to say?

5
00:00:07.700 --> 00:00:09.666
If you really want to let go of my uncle

6
00:00:09.666 --> 00:00:11.266
Instead of hiding

7
00:00:11.266 --> 00:00:13.966
The more you avoid it, the more you care.

8
00:00:15.266 --> 00:00:17.633
I want to have a good talk with him

9
00:00:18.966 --> 00:00:21.500
Gu Sijun, you have been hiding for four years

10
00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:22.966
I also hid for four years

11
00:00:23.100 --> 00:00:26.633
This ridiculous relationship should be over for good

12
00:00:27.966 --> 00:00:29.433
Let's have a good talk

13
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:32.533
How were your years in England?

14
00:00:32.533 --> 00:00:34.366
Very good, Xue Feng has been with me

15
00:00:34.366 --> 00:00:37.066
Then I have to thank him for taking such good care of you.

16
00:00:37.166 --> 00:00:39.766
What status do you have to thank his uncle?

17
00:00:39.766 --> 00:00:41.466
Lolo, am I wrong?

18
00:00:41.466 --> 00:00:43.033
You are just my uncle

19
00:00:43.266 --> 00:00:45.600
No? I know.

20
00:00:46.066 --> 00:00:47.166
Are you still complaining about me?

21
00:00:47.166 --> 00:00:47.966
No complaints

22
00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:50.666
I shouldn't have been in love with you back then

23
00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:52.400
Now I've figured it out.

24
00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:54.633
So please don't cross the line again

25
00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:56.633
Do the wrong thing

